      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly in such great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved, super dependable, and is ready to hit the road for some new adventures with you. It drives smoothly and has been kept very clean. You\u2019re going to love how it feels behind the wheel\u2014come take it for a spin!",
