    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features the high-revving 3.4L M97 flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine architecture provides a low polar moment of inertia, ensuring exceptional turn-in response and chassis balance. This example is equipped with PASM active damping and four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers for consistent thermal management. Recent maintenance includes a proactive replacement of the water pump and air-oil separator (AOS). While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains mechanically dialed and the structural integrity is excellent.",
